&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain category strategy, in service of company-wide goals&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the identification, evaluation, and choice of suppliers and SKUs for the category&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate, negotiate, and manage RFPs with both new and current suppliers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strategic supplier partnerships that foster innovation, improve performance, reduce cost, and strengthen long-term supply continuity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct supply market analysis and collect supplier intelligence to drive sourcing process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with culinary team to identify new ingredient needs and test new suppliers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with Cross Functional Partners to ensure all new suppliers meet Home Chef guidelines and expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as point on highly visible new protein A/B and Market tests&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with legal to negotiate contract terms with key supplier partners and ensure terms + conditions of those contracts are managed and met&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with Procurement Operations, Warehouse and site teams to improve supply chain performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with local sites and supplier partners to problem solve regular supply disruptions and secure product in time for weekly meal production&lt;/li&gt;
