&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach, train, and develop a multi-shift FSQA team to ensure they possess in-depth knowledge of both raw meal kit and RTH safety principles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Production, Warehouse, and Continuous Improvement to integrate food safety into the facility&#39;s daily operational DNA.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategically build a talent pipeline at the site level to support business growth and technical complexity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Multi-Platform Governance &amp;amp; Project Management&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the implementation of Home Chef and SQF standards for both business platforms, ensuring consistent compliance with FDA and USDA requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the site SME for FSQA programs, overseeing program pilots, validations, and readiness assessments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary point of contact for all regulatory and third-party inspections, managing CAPA activities and systemic root cause investigations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Strategic Improvement &amp;amp; Risk Assessment&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize internal and customer-reported data to identify trends and execute strategic initiatives that reduce errors and enhance the customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
