&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2013, Home Chef is the leading meal solutions company with both a retail and online presence. Available online at&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://homechef.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=http://homechef.com/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1725544177877000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0x0MVCSCH1-PeH3T0UFaU_&quot;&gt;homechef.com&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and in retail at more than 2,100 Kroger grocery stores, Home Chef is committed to inspiring and enabling more people to cook simple, delicious meals, no matter how busy they are.&lt;/p&gt;
