&lt;p&gt;This role follows a &lt;strong&gt;2nd&lt;/strong&gt; shift schedule, working from &lt;strong&gt;3:30 PM to 12:30 AM&lt;/strong&gt;, with designated days off on &lt;strong&gt;Saturday and Sunday.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensures the Food Safety and quality of all product labeled, portioned, cooked, MAP, packaged, and shipped from Home Chef Tempo by working alongside production to conduct on-the-line checks of product against recipe specifications and quality standards.&lt;/p&gt;
